ActFirst Nations Goods and Services Tax Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 1 to the First Nations Goods and Services Tax Act, No. 2009-1
PrecisORDER AMENDING SCHEDULE 1 TO THE FIRST NATIONS GOODS AND SERVICES TAX ACT by adding the name of six First Nations along with the name of the governing body of each First Nation and the description of each First Nation’s reserves, where the First Nation’s GST-type tax may apply.
